data.name: SURGICAL GOWNS
data.description:
## COMPOSITION
- 100% Non Woven (Polyphenylenether – PPE) fabric made of Viscose and Polyester Fibers

## STERILIZATION
- Ethylene Oxide (EO) Sterile

## PRESENTATIONS
- Latex free
- White and Blue
- Wide Range of Different Materials Compounds and Size
- Elastic Wrist

## PERFORMANCE
- Highly Breathable material
- Fluid repellent / Full permeability
- Comfortable and soft fabric

## PROTECTION
- DENTAL
